annotate.ResultsPage: this page should be presented as result of search function call

SearchForm.value: object representing search component and its functionality

getGoButton.value: function encapsulating access to submit button of search form

getSearchInput.value: function encapsulating access to search input field - here you should enter search queries

annotate.doSearch: launch search functionality for given search query

SearchResultsRow.value: object representing result row which is used on  results page
